rComments: Best spanish teacher I've ever had, really wish he hadn't switched schools.

A wonderful professor. Had a blast every class - he was very inclusive and would always take questions from anyone, no matter how many times the same question was asked. Would highly recommend him to anyone who wants to learn Spanish!!
Really good prof. He is really funny and good at making you not feel stupid. He loves spanish and it shows in his teaching.

Makes you practice without making you making you feel stupid for not knowing how to speak spanish properly. His evaluations were fair and his expectations were realistic. No complaints whatsoever - I highly recommend him to anyone
